```jsx
function CustomButton({ variant, loading, onPress, children, disabled }) {
  const mode = variant === 'primary' ? 'contained' : 'outlined';
  return (
    <Button mode={mode} onPress={onPress} disabled={disabled || loading} loading={loading}>
      {children}
    </Button>
  );
}
```
La prop `loading` de Paper Button intègre un spinner automatiquement.

